<document><title><tag>row</tag> component</title>

<section><title>Associated Attributes</title>
<ul>
  <li><attr>rowNum</attr>  <em>(text)</em></li>
  <li><attr>header</attr>  <em>(boolean)</em></li>
  <li><attr>halign</attr>  <em>(text)</em></li>
  <li><attr>valign</attr>  <em>(text)</em></li>
  <li><attr>left</attr>  <em>(text)</em></li>
  <li><attr>bottom</attr>  <em>(text)</em></li>

</ul>

</section>


<section><title>Description</title>
<!--use <ref> on all component names (other than the one indexed from this file) in this section only-->
  <p>The <tag>row</tag><idx><tag>row</tag></idx> component is a row container element for the individual <ref uri="doenet:doenetId=jN7vEZ4h2eNuuvNYlBO-Q"><tag>cell</tag></ref> elements of  a <ref uri="doenet:doenetId=Bm5kSKo8GvPyl85lokH8_"><tag>tabular</tag></ref>.   See examples below.</p>
</section> 

  
<section><title>Usage Examples</title>

<subsection><title>Example 1: <tag>row</tag> with <attr>header</attr></title>
<p>In the code below, the <tag>row</tag> component is used in the standard manner, nested inside a <ref uri="doenet:doenetId=Bm5kSKo8GvPyl85lokH8_"><tag>tabular</tag></ref> component. 
 The <attr>header</attr> attribute is specified to indicate a row with bold text. (See also, <ref uri="doenet:doenetId=zRuXlzQ0_iNqNqZHHQMxG"><tag>table</tag></ref>, <ref uri="doenet:doenetId=5HERf7liZuJ_-NnhzeTaU"><tag>title</tag></ref>.)</p>  
<example boxed="true"><title>Sample DoenetML code (Example 1)</title>
<pre>
  
&lt;table&gt;&lt;title&gt;Fake Weather Statistics&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;tabular&gt;
    &lt;row header&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;Time&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;Mon&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;Tue&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;Wed&lt;/cell&gt;
    &lt;/row&gt;
          
    &lt;row&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;🌧&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;❄️&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;☀️&lt;/cell&gt;
    &lt;/row&gt;
        
    &lt;row&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;AM&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;rain&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;snow&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;sunny&lt;/cell&gt;
    &lt;/row&gt;
          
    &lt;row&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;50&lt;m&gt;^{\circ}&lt;/m&gt;&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;15&lt;m&gt;^{\circ}&lt;/m&gt;&lt;/cell&gt;
      &lt;cell&gt;-10&lt;m&gt;^{\circ}&lt;/m&gt;&lt;/cell&gt;
    &lt;/row&gt;
  &lt;/tabular&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

</pre>
  </example>
</subsection>

